MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 3266580948191850374}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 45b840e1187fd2d4fa1d6e0e9109c806, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  dayLength: 3
  timerHand: {fileID: 2816361838123723365}
  timerFill: {fileID: 953722136587426502}
  clockText: {fileID: 478809641021206042}
  digitalText: {fileID: 7879915914029814958}
  dayStartOverlay: {fileID: 4741392036497951600}
  panelExplanation: {fileID: 995177306874361535}
  dayExplanation:
  - Today's your first day running the shop on your own! Fulfill potion orders for
    the customers. Check the recipe book if you need reminders of recipes!
  - Oh no! A spilled potion turned the floor into slippery ice! No time to clean;
    you have potions to make!
  - A new ingredient! The mandrake root is sentient plant that screams when it is
    uprooted. Check the recipe book for new recipes!
  - Gah! The cauldrons absorbed a Potion of Sentience and now they're floating around!
    You have to chase them if you want to brew anything...
  - A new ingredient! Basilisk eyes are from a large, deadly, snow dwelling lizard
    with eight legs. Check the recipe book for new recipes!
  - How did this happen?! The Goblin got out of his cage! You could have sworn you
    locked it. Too bad goblin control is a town away...
  - A new ingredient! Rabbit feet, while normally mundane, have major reactions with
    other magical ingredients. Check the recipe book for new recipes!
  - "Brrr! A wind storm blew your windows open! Now you have to deal with strong
    gusts blowing you and your ingredients around\u2026"
  - A new ingredient! Troll bones exhibit strong regenerative properties even after
    the troll has died. Check the recipe book for new recipes!
  - "Yuck! Master\u2019s snail in-laws stopped by to give you a hug, and now you\u2019re
    covered in their sticky slime. Right as you open up shop too\u2026"
  startDaySfx: {fileID: 8300000, guid: da32e896bb83a1a4a922b1eb83cb258d, type: 3}
  endDaySfx: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 232f504a7739c1f429065a8f60337c66, type: 3}
